WEBVTT

01:46.125 --> 01:48.500
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:48.500 --> 01:51.250
SO IF YOU OR THAT SKINNY BITCH
TRY TO SCREW WITH WHAT'S MINE,

01:51.250 --> 01:54.166
I SWEAR TO GOD, I DON'T CARE
WHO I HAVE TO HURT.

01:54.166 --> 01:57.291
Dexter: LET'S FACE IT, PAUL.
YOU'VE GOT A PROBLEM.

01:57.291 --> 01:59.041
IT'S TIME FOR YOU TO GO AWAY.

01:59.041 --> 02:01.000
Rita: IT'S PAUL.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.250
HE VIOLATED FLORIDA'S
THREE-STRIKES LAW.

02:03.250 --> 02:06.250
THE COPS PICKED HIM UP
TOTALLY STRUNG OUT ON HEROIN.

02:06.250 --> 02:08.959
[ Chuckling ]
HE'S BACK IN JAIL.

02:08.959 --> 02:10.875
[ LAUGHING ]

02:10.875 --> 02:12.959
HOLY SHIT!
THEY'RE FUCKING FINGERTIPS.

02:12.959 --> 02:16.166
HE STARTED GETTING ALL ROUGH
WITH ME UNTIL HE SAW THIS.

02:16.166 --> 02:17.458
THEN WHAT?

02:17.458 --> 02:19.792
THEN HE CHANGED HIS TUNE,
GOT ALL TURNED ON.

02:19.792 --> 02:21.959
TOLD ME
TO TAKE MY FAKE HAND OFF.

02:21.959 --> 02:23.709
HE TAKES ALL MY NAIL POLISH

02:23.709 --> 02:25.458
AND PAINTS EACH NAIL
A DIFFERENT COLOR.

02:25.458 --> 02:27.625
MENTHOL?
LIKE COUGH DROPS.

02:27.625 --> 02:31.125
I COULD HEAR THEM CLICKING
AGAINST HIS TEETH WHEN HE...

02:31.125 --> 02:33.667
SON OF A BITCH LOVED
THOSE FUCKING LOZENGES.

02:33.667 --> 02:35.792
I WAS CONFUSED
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

02:35.792 --> 02:37.625
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

02:37.625 --> 02:39.417
I LOVE YOU.

02:39.417 --> 02:41.959
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

02:44.333 --> 02:45.875
OW.

02:45.875 --> 02:47.792
WHAT?
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR LIP?

02:47.792 --> 02:49.375
[ CAR ALARM BEEPS ]

02:51.000 --> 02:52.834
AAH!
[ CAR ALARM ACTIVATES ]

02:52.834 --> 02:55.500
NO, IT'S -- I HAD AN INCIDENT
WITH A TOOL AT THE WORKSHOP.

02:55.500 --> 02:58.000
OHH!

03:04.125 --> 03:06.500
Man: I NEED AN AMBULANCE
AT 1228 CALENDAR STREET.

03:06.500 --> 03:07.834
A GUY'S BEEN STABBED.

03:22.834 --> 03:26.041
Dexter: I'VE NEVER HAD MUCH USE
FOR THE CONCEPT OF HELL,

03:26.041 --> 03:28.458
BUT IF HELL EXISTS, I'M IN IT.

03:35.875 --> 03:39.125
THE SAME IMAGES RUNNING
THROUGH MY HEAD OVER AND OVER.

03:39.125 --> 03:40.250
[ SCREAMS ]

03:50.208 --> 03:52.083
I WAS THERE.

03:52.083 --> 03:53.083
AAH!

03:53.083 --> 03:55.208
I SAW MY MOTHER'S DEATH.

03:55.208 --> 03:56.458
[ CHAIN SAW REVVING ]

03:56.458 --> 03:57.667
AAH!

03:57.667 --> 04:00.083
A BURIED MEMORY,
FORGOTTEN ALL THESE YEARS.

04:00.083 --> 04:02.792
IT CLIMBED INSIDE ME THAT DAY.

04:02.792 --> 04:05.500
AND IT'S BEEN WITH ME
EVER SINCE --

04:05.500 --> 04:08.834
MY DARK PASSENGER.

04:17.417 --> 04:19.875
YOU SHOULD BE
FOCUSING ON ME, SOCIO.

04:19.875 --> 04:22.375
[ Echoing ] YOU SHOULD BE
FOCUSING ON ME, SOCIO.

04:24.792 --> 04:26.667
SERIOUSLY WANT TO GET
THE MOTHERFUCKER

04:26.667 --> 04:27.917
THAT DID THIS TO BATISTA.

04:32.792 --> 04:34.542
HEY.
YOU ALL RIGHT?

04:34.542 --> 04:36.667
YEAH.
I'M OKAY.

04:36.667 --> 04:39.125
I'M JUST, YOU KNOW,
DISTRAUGHT ABOUT ANGEL.

04:39.125 --> 04:41.875
HOW'S HE DOING?
DO WE KNOW?

04:41.875 --> 04:43.834
STILL IN SURGERY.

04:43.834 --> 04:45.500
LaGUERTA'S THERE.

04:45.500 --> 04:48.250
GOD, I HATE FEELING
SO HELPLESS.

04:49.792 --> 04:52.959
WHAT, NO JOKES ABOUT PROVIDING
GROSS SEXUAL COMFORT

04:52.959 --> 04:54.417
IN A TIME OF CRISIS?

04:54.417 --> 04:55.625
OUR FRIEND WAS STABBED...

04:55.625 --> 04:58.000
AND HE MIGHT DIE.

04:58.000 --> 04:59.917
OFFICER MORGAN.

05:05.000 --> 05:06.667
WHAT DO YOU THINK, DEX?

05:06.667 --> 05:09.375
HE PUT UP A FIGHT.
THERE WAS A STRUGGLE.

05:09.375 --> 05:10.959
ATTABOY, ANGEL.

05:10.959 --> 05:14.834
HERE, THIS TRAIL --
STEADY STREAM OF DROPS.

05:14.834 --> 05:18.667
HE HAD A FEW SECONDS.
TRIED TO MOVE AWAY UNTIL --

05:18.667 --> 05:20.583
TILL HE FELL.

05:22.583 --> 05:24.750
SO MUCH BLOOD.

05:30.875 --> 05:33.166
WHAT'S HAPPENING TO ME?

05:48.458 --> 05:53.041
♪ PORQUE TOCAN NUESTRA CANCIóN ♪

05:53.041 --> 05:58.834
♪ BALADA DE LOS DOS, SUFRO MáS ♪

05:58.834 --> 06:01.166
NO WAY.

06:01.166 --> 06:03.750
YOU'RE THE ONE
I'M SUPPOSED TO MEET.

06:03.750 --> 06:05.250
IN THE FLESH.

06:05.250 --> 06:08.083
YOU KNOW, I WAS JUST TALKING
TO SOMEONE ABOUT YOU.

06:08.083 --> 06:09.500
HMM.

06:09.500 --> 06:11.458
WHAT'S UP?

06:15.625 --> 06:17.417
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:17.417 --> 06:19.792
THAT TICKLES.

06:19.792 --> 06:22.291
DON'T STOP.

06:22.291 --> 06:25.208
I WOULDN'T DREAM
OF STOPPING.

06:25.208 --> 06:27.875
YOU'RE SO DIFFERENT
THIS TIME --

06:27.875 --> 06:29.500
GENTLE.

06:29.500 --> 06:31.875
I THOUGHT YOU WERE GONNA
TRY AND GET ALL PERVY

06:31.875 --> 06:33.750
WITH MY STUMP AGAIN.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.875
ACTUALLY,
YOUR...IMPERFECTION

06:35.875 --> 06:38.041
IS WHAT SAVED YOU
THE FIRST TIME.

06:38.041 --> 06:39.834
SAVED ME FROM WHAT?

06:39.834 --> 06:42.583
TRUE ARTISTRY.

06:45.000 --> 06:49.291
THE MESSAGE OF MY WORK
IS NOT IN THE PRODUCT ITSELF,

06:49.291 --> 06:53.375
BUT RATHER
THE PRESENTATION.

06:53.375 --> 06:55.875
THAT WRINKLED FLESH
ON YOUR RADIAL CARPAL JOINT

06:55.875 --> 06:57.208
IS FAR FROM PERFECT.

06:57.208 --> 06:59.250
IT'S QUITE UNSIGHTLY,
ACTUALLY.

06:59.250 --> 07:01.417
HEY, YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE
AN ASSHOLE ABOUT IT.

07:01.417 --> 07:02.834
HEY, HEY,
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

07:02.834 --> 07:05.166
Shh, Shh, Shh,
Shh, Shh, Shh.

07:05.166 --> 07:08.625
I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO OFFEND.

07:08.625 --> 07:09.959
[ SIGHS ]

07:09.959 --> 07:12.417
TRUTHFULLY...

07:12.417 --> 07:15.959
I'M THANKFUL FOR YOU.

07:15.959 --> 07:17.750
YOU'RE MY ESCAPE PLAN.

07:17.750 --> 07:21.083
ESCAPE FROM WHAT?

07:21.083 --> 07:23.083
THE POLICE.

07:23.083 --> 07:26.917
BECAUSE OF YOU, I'VE HAD
TO SPEED UP MY PROJECT.

07:26.917 --> 07:29.375
I NEED SOMETHING
TO DISTRACT THEM BY.

07:29.375 --> 07:32.083
AND I ALWAYS FOUND
A FRESHLY CHOPPED-UP BODY

07:32.083 --> 07:33.542
ALWAYS DOES THE TRICK.

07:33.542 --> 07:35.750
WAIT, WAIT! NO!

07:35.750 --> 07:38.917
DON'T STRUGGLE.
THAT NEVER HELPS.

07:38.917 --> 07:40.875
I'M COMPRESSING
YOUR CAROTID ARTERY,

07:40.875 --> 07:44.375
AND THAT IS CUTTING OFF
OXYGEN TO YOUR BRAIN.

07:44.375 --> 07:48.125
IN ABOUT 10 SECONDS,
YOU'LL BE UNCONSCIOUS.

08:06.208 --> 08:08.417
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

08:14.625 --> 08:17.250
Rudy: HEY, IT'S RUDY.
LEAVE A MESSAGE.

08:17.250 --> 08:19.000
OKAY,
I GUESS YOU WENT TO BED.

08:19.000 --> 08:22.500
OR YOU FELL ASLEEP ON THE COUCH
WATCHING "XENA" RERUNS,

08:22.500 --> 08:24.834
WHICH I STILL THINK
MAKES YOU A DORK.

08:27.667 --> 08:29.917
EITHER WAY,
CALL ME WHEN YOU GET THIS, OKAY?

08:29.917 --> 08:33.166
MISS YOU.

08:33.166 --> 08:34.667
HE'S STILL IN SURGERY,

08:34.667 --> 08:37.291
BUT I DON'T KNOW
WHEN WE'LL HEAR ANYTHING.

08:37.291 --> 08:39.583
SO I GUESS YOU WON'T BE
COMING OVER TONIGHT.

08:39.583 --> 08:42.000
NO.
I MEAN, I CAN'T.

08:42.000 --> 08:43.458
I understand.

08:43.458 --> 08:45.333
You need to be there
for your friend.

08:45.333 --> 08:48.166
I HAVEN'T TOLD THE KIDS YET.

08:48.166 --> 08:49.625
TOLD THEM ABOUT ANGEL?

08:49.625 --> 08:53.417
NO, ABOUT PAUL...
BEING BACK IN PRISON?

08:53.417 --> 08:55.041
I hate
breaking their hearts.

08:55.041 --> 08:56.792
They think so much
of their dad now, and --

08:56.792 --> 08:58.458
RIGHT.

09:00.500 --> 09:03.875
YOU KNOW WHAT?

09:03.875 --> 09:06.709
FOCUS ON ANGEL.
WE CAN TALK ABOUT THIS LATER.

09:06.709 --> 09:08.083
THANKS.

09:08.083 --> 09:10.667
THEY'RE ACTUALLY COMING OUT
RIGHT NOW. I GOT TO GO.

09:20.959 --> 09:22.792
[ SIGHS ]

09:22.792 --> 09:25.959
ANGEL SUSTAINED
SEVERE INTERNAL INJURIES.

09:25.959 --> 09:28.542
HE LOST A LOT OF BLOOD.

09:28.542 --> 09:31.917
BUT...THE SURGERY
WAS SUCCESSFUL.

09:31.917 --> 09:35.500
IT LOOKS LIKE OUR BOY'S
OUT OF THE WOODS.

09:40.333 --> 09:44.917
Dexter: I KNOW I SHOULD STAY,
BE A PART OF THE GROUP HUG.

09:44.917 --> 09:47.125
BUT I CAN'T FOCUS.

09:47.125 --> 09:49.750
I'M TRAPPED IN THE CLUTCHES
OF A MEMORY.

09:49.750 --> 09:52.041
I NEED TO KNOW WHAT IT MEANS.

10:00.333 --> 10:02.792
MORGAN.

10:02.792 --> 10:06.125
WHAT THE FUCK
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

10:06.125 --> 10:08.542
I HAVE SOMEPLACE
I HAVE TO BE.

10:08.542 --> 10:09.917
OH.

10:09.917 --> 10:11.792
WELL, WE ALL GOT
SOMEPLACE TO BE.

10:11.792 --> 10:13.667
BUT YOU JUST FOUND OUT

10:13.667 --> 10:15.583
THAT SOMEBODY WHO WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE YOUR FRIEND IS GONNA LIVE.

10:15.583 --> 10:17.583
DOES THAT MAKE YOU
FEEL ANYTHING?

10:17.583 --> 10:21.375
ANYTHING AT ALL?

10:21.375 --> 10:23.875
TAKE YOUR FUCKING HAND
OFF ME.

10:28.208 --> 10:31.583
JUST WHAT
I ALWAYS THOUGHT.

10:31.583 --> 10:33.291
RIGHT.

10:38.667 --> 10:41.208
♪ DECK THE HALLS
WITH PARTS OF BODIES ♪

10:41.208 --> 10:42.458
♪ LA-DA-DA-DA DUM ♪

10:42.458 --> 10:44.583
[ HUMMING ]

10:59.875 --> 11:03.291
[ BUZZER SOUNDS ]

11:03.291 --> 11:06.417
SHIT.
JUST WHAT I NEED.

11:11.667 --> 11:12.667
[ BUZZER ]

11:20.834 --> 11:22.417
HEY.

11:22.417 --> 11:23.834
I KNOW IT'S LATE.

11:23.834 --> 11:26.333
I GUESS YOU DIDN'T GET
MY MESSAGE.

11:26.333 --> 11:30.166
I DROVE BY
AND SAW YOUR CAR.

11:30.166 --> 11:31.583
I CAN GO.

11:31.583 --> 11:33.417
GET YOUR ASS IN HERE.

11:33.417 --> 11:37.125
IT'S ABOUT TIME
YOU SEE WHERE I LIVE ANYWAY.

11:37.125 --> 11:40.125
OH, YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW MUCH I NEEDED THIS.

11:40.125 --> 11:42.291
YOU FEEL GOOD.

11:42.291 --> 11:44.500
AND COLD --
YOU'RE FREEZING.

11:44.500 --> 11:47.542
WELL, THEN STAY
AND KEEP ME WARM.

11:54.709 --> 11:56.333
MMM.

12:01.542 --> 12:04.208
THIS BATISTA THING
HAS GOTTEN TO YOU, HASN'T IT?

12:06.834 --> 12:09.500
ANGEL'S DAUGHTER WAS THERE.

12:11.083 --> 12:13.625
THAT'S GOT TO BE ROUGH.

12:13.625 --> 12:17.417
DAUGHTER OF A COP --
JUST LIKE YOU.

12:19.083 --> 12:21.083
YEAH.

12:21.083 --> 12:23.291
I REMEMBER
WHAT THAT'S LIKE --

12:23.291 --> 12:24.917
KISSING YOUR FATHER GOODBYE,

12:24.917 --> 12:27.458
ALWAYS AFRAID
IT'S FOR THE LAST TIME.

12:27.458 --> 12:28.625
HEY...

12:28.625 --> 12:31.083
LET'S GET OUT OF TOWN
FOR THE WEEKEND --

12:31.083 --> 12:33.333
JUST THE TWO OF US.

12:33.333 --> 12:36.208
WE NEED TO TALK.

12:40.041 --> 12:43.125
I'M SITTING RIGHT HERE.

12:43.125 --> 12:44.667
NOPE.

12:44.667 --> 12:47.250
THE TIME
HAS GOT TO BE RIGHT.

12:50.083 --> 12:51.625
OKAY.

12:51.625 --> 12:54.583
IT'LL HAVE TO WAIT...

12:54.583 --> 12:58.583
AT LEAST TILL WE CATCH THE
ASSHOLE WHO DID THIS TO BATISTA.

12:58.583 --> 13:02.041
LET ME WARN YOU --
I CAN BE VERY PERSISTENT.

13:02.041 --> 13:03.709
I NEED TO GET OUT OF TOWN,

13:03.709 --> 13:07.583
AND I NEED YOU
TO COME WITH ME.

13:07.583 --> 13:10.291
MM-HMM.

13:10.291 --> 13:14.750
WHAT I NEED IS SLEEP,
WHICH IS NOT GONNA BE EASY.

13:14.750 --> 13:17.709
I'M TOTALLY WIRED
FROM ALL THIS SHIT.

13:17.709 --> 13:21.458
WELL, LUCKY FOR YOU,
I HAVE THE PERFECT CURE.

13:21.458 --> 13:23.792
MY LOVING ARMS.

13:23.792 --> 13:25.959
[ CHUCKLING ]

13:25.959 --> 13:29.667
AND...I GOT A LITTLE THING
TO HELP YOU SLEEP.

13:29.667 --> 13:32.375
THAT AIN'T
NO LITTLE THING.

13:32.375 --> 13:33.542
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

13:33.542 --> 13:34.959
I MEANT VALIUM.

13:34.959 --> 13:37.417
IT'S ONE OF THE PERKS
WORKING AT THE HOSPITAL.

13:37.417 --> 13:40.458
WINE AND VALIUM?

13:40.458 --> 13:42.458
I'LL BE TOTALLY HELPLESS.

13:42.458 --> 13:43.750
YOU READ MY MIND.

13:45.834 --> 13:47.458
[ GIGGLING ]

14:07.041 --> 14:08.208
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

14:10.500 --> 14:12.166
[ BELL DINGS ]

14:12.166 --> 14:13.959
WELL,
AS I LIVE AND BREATHE.

14:13.959 --> 14:15.500
YOU MISS ME?

14:15.500 --> 14:18.166
YOU AND THE BEAR CLAWS
YOU'RE HIDING BEHIND YOUR BACK.

14:18.166 --> 14:19.542
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:19.542 --> 14:22.375
THIS MUST BE IMPORTANT.

14:22.375 --> 14:24.458
HAVEN'T SEEN
MUCH OF YOU LATELY.

14:24.458 --> 14:27.083
NO REST FOR THE WICKED.

14:27.083 --> 14:28.500
HOW'S GENE?

14:28.500 --> 14:30.834
GOOD DAYS AND BAD.

14:30.834 --> 14:33.834
HE JUST FINISHED HIS FIRST ROUND
OF RADIATION.

14:33.834 --> 14:36.375
WELL, HE'S A GOOD GUY.

14:36.375 --> 14:38.667
NOT MUCH OF A BRIDGE PLAYER,
THOUGH.

14:38.667 --> 14:41.000
[ Chuckling ] HARRY AND GENE
USED TO GET SO MAD

14:41.000 --> 14:43.709
EVERY TIME DORIS AND I
WOULD TAKE THEM TO THE CLEANERS.

14:43.709 --> 14:47.041
[ CHUCKLING ]

14:47.041 --> 14:49.917
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD DIG UP
AN OLD CASE FILE FOR ME.

14:49.917 --> 14:52.333
WELL, SURE THING.
GOT A DATE?

14:52.333 --> 14:54.375
UH, NOT EXACTLY.

14:54.375 --> 14:58.375
IT'S THE CRIME SCENE
WHERE HARRY FOUND ME.

15:00.667 --> 15:03.875
UH...I WISH I COULD HELP,
BUT...

15:03.875 --> 15:05.625
EVERYTHING FROM THAT LONG AGO

15:05.625 --> 15:08.375
IS BOXED UP IN THE BASEMENT
AT CITY HALL.

15:08.375 --> 15:10.375
AND...AS YOU CAN SEE,

15:10.375 --> 15:14.083
I'M UP TO MY YOU-KNOW-WHAT
IN YEAR-END REPORTS, SO...

15:14.083 --> 15:15.834
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

15:19.125 --> 15:21.792
IT'S MY LIEUTENANT.

15:24.041 --> 15:26.250
CAMILLA, IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU REMEMBER?

15:26.250 --> 15:30.417
WHAT I REMEMBER, DEXTER MORGAN,
IS YOUR FATHER CARING ENOUGH

15:30.417 --> 15:34.417
TO BRING YOU INTO HIS HOME
AND GIVE YOU A LOVING FAMILY.

15:34.417 --> 15:38.542
I WOULDN'T KEEP
YOUR LIEUTENANT WAITING.

15:41.875 --> 15:44.000
WHO FOUND THE BODY PARTS?

15:44.000 --> 15:46.250
I DID. THEY WERE LEFT
UNDER THE TREE.

15:46.250 --> 15:48.125
I THOUGHT IT WAS THE CREW
FROM LAST NIGHT

15:48.125 --> 15:51.375
JUST MESSING AROUND...
TILL I FOUND THE HEAD.

15:51.375 --> 15:53.166
I TOLD HIM
NOT TO TOUCH ANYTHING,

15:53.166 --> 15:54.917
BUT HE NEVER LISTENS.

15:54.917 --> 15:56.542
GOD, PATTY,
YOU'RE SUCH A BITCH.

15:56.542 --> 15:58.583
DID YOU GUYS SEE ANYTHING
OUT OF THE ORDINARY

15:58.583 --> 16:00.166
BEFORE YOU FOUND
THE BODY?

16:00.166 --> 16:03.125
THERE WERE SOME BROKEN
ORNAMENTS BY THE TREE.

16:03.125 --> 16:07.875
WHO COULD DO SOMETHING LIKE THIS
SO CLOSE TO CHRISTMAS?

16:07.875 --> 16:09.875
THE GRINCH.

16:09.875 --> 16:11.959
OH, YOU'RE A FUCKING
RIOT, MAX!

16:11.959 --> 16:14.375
LIKE ANYONE'S GONNA GO SHOPPING
DOWN HERE AFTER THIS.

16:14.375 --> 16:15.792
THERE GO OUR JOBS.

16:16.083 --> 16:19.583
THANK YOU FOR
YOUR COOPERATION.

16:19.583 --> 16:23.458
OH, SUCKS TO BE AN ELF.
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:23.458 --> 16:25.417
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

16:28.458 --> 16:30.166
GET SOME VISUAL SURVEILLANCE.

16:30.166 --> 16:32.709
I GOT HERE AS FAST AS I COULD.
WHAT ARE WE LOOKING AT?

16:32.709 --> 16:34.667
FEMALE VICTIM
CUT UP INTO PIECES.

16:34.667 --> 16:36.291
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?
SO SOON?

16:36.291 --> 16:38.375
YEP, AND AFTER THE BLOODBATH
AT THE HOTEL,

16:38.375 --> 16:40.208
CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
HOW THE CAPTAIN'S

16:40.208 --> 16:42.250
GONNA HANDLE THE PRESS
ON THIS ONE.

16:42.250 --> 16:44.792
JAMES, I NEED YOU TO WALK DEXTER
TO THE CRIME SCENE.

16:44.792 --> 16:47.166
AND WILL SOMEBODY TURN OFF
THIS GODDAMN SNOW MACHINE?!

16:47.166 --> 16:50.250
YOUR SISTER
CAN HELP YOU OUT.

16:50.250 --> 16:53.208
THAT A WHOLE SEXUAL-TENSION
THING OR AM I MISSING SOMETHING?

16:55.375 --> 16:57.333
103.

16:57.333 --> 16:59.834
IT'S THE SAME NUMBERS
HE LEFT AT MARINA VIEW HOTEL.

16:59.834 --> 17:01.667
ANY LEADS
AS TO WHAT THEY MEAN?

17:01.667 --> 17:04.291
WE'VE TALKED TO NUMEROLOGISTS,
MATHEMATICIANS,

17:04.291 --> 17:07.125
CODE BREAKERS -- NOTHING.
THEY NEED MORE TO GO ON.

17:09.375 --> 17:12.000
FIRST HE TURNS
MY WHOLE WORLD INSIDE OUT

17:12.000 --> 17:13.500
WITH A CARNIVAL OF BLOOD.

17:16.959 --> 17:19.083
NOW HE LEAVES ME THIS --

17:19.083 --> 17:22.834
A CALMING OASIS IN THE DESERT
OF MY CONFUSION.

17:22.834 --> 17:25.041
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

17:31.667 --> 17:33.750
CRIME SCENE'S WIPED CLEAN.

17:33.750 --> 17:35.291
ANOTHER HOOKER?

17:35.291 --> 17:37.709
HO, HO, HO --
ANOTHER DEAD HO.

17:37.709 --> 17:39.208
SOMEBODY'S BEEN NAUGHTY.

17:39.208 --> 17:41.625
HEY, MORGAN, WANT TO SIT
ON MY LAP WHEN WE'RE DONE

17:41.625 --> 17:43.625
AND TELL ME WHAT YOU WANT
FOR CHRISTMAS?

17:43.625 --> 17:44.917
AND HE'S BACK.

17:44.917 --> 17:46.542
NO, THANKS.

17:46.542 --> 17:50.208
LAST THING ON MY WISH LIST IS
A BURNING SENSATION WHEN I PEE.

17:50.208 --> 17:52.625
THIS DOESN'T SEEM RIGHT.

17:52.625 --> 17:55.500
BODY PARTS SCATTERED
AMONG THE PRESENTS.

17:55.500 --> 17:57.041
BROKEN ORNAMENTS.

17:57.041 --> 18:00.667
IT'S NOT HIS USUAL
METICULOUS STYLE.

18:00.667 --> 18:03.500
IT SEEMS RUSHED...

18:03.500 --> 18:05.041
HAPHAZARD.

18:05.041 --> 18:07.208
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN WHY WE CAN'T
FIND ONE OF THE HANDS.

18:13.667 --> 18:14.834
WHAT'S WRONG?

18:14.834 --> 18:17.208
THERE'S SOMETHING
UNDERNEATH THE TORSO.

18:23.125 --> 18:25.583
MERRY CHRISTMAS, MIAMI.

18:25.583 --> 18:27.291
Woman:
AFTER ALL THIS TIME,

18:27.291 --> 18:29.542
WHY DO YOU THINK THE ICE-TRUCK
KILLER HAS STRUCK AGAIN?

18:29.542 --> 18:32.709
ANY ANSWER AT THIS TIME WOULD BE
PURE SPECULATION ON MY PART.

18:32.709 --> 18:34.583
DO YOU THINK
IT HAS ANY CONNECTION

18:34.583 --> 18:37.166
WITH YOUR DEPARTMENT'S HANDLING
OF THE NEIL PERRY FIASCO?

18:37.166 --> 18:38.542
SIR?

18:45.417 --> 18:47.041
[ BREATHING HEAVILY  ]

18:47.041 --> 18:49.458
YOU'VE ARRESTED
THE WRONG MAN.

18:49.458 --> 18:52.083
MAY THE WORLD THINK
I'M A RANK AMATEUR,

18:52.083 --> 18:57.667
AND I'M VERY, VERY ANGRY
TO ANSWER FOR YOUR MISTAKES.

18:57.667 --> 18:59.375
[ CRYING  ]

18:59.375 --> 19:00.625
STOP THE TAPE.

19:00.625 --> 19:02.208
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

19:02.208 --> 19:03.625
LOOK AT HER TEARS.
THEY'RE ROLLING UP.

19:03.625 --> 19:06.458
Maria: OH, MY GOD.

19:06.458 --> 19:09.083
BASTARD'S GOT HER
UPSIDE DOWN.

19:09.083 --> 19:11.250
Dexter:
THAT'S HOW HE BLEEDS THEM OUT.

19:11.250 --> 19:13.083
HE STRINGS THEM UP LIKE MEAT.

19:17.000 --> 19:18.166
[ CRYING  ]

19:19.458 --> 19:21.667
IT WAS ME.

19:22.709 --> 19:24.458
OH, GOD, NO.

19:24.458 --> 19:26.750
NO, PLEASE, NO --

19:26.750 --> 19:28.041
[ GASPING  ]

19:28.041 --> 19:30.000
Matthews:
ALL RIGHT, TURN IT OFF.

19:30.000 --> 19:32.291
I'LL HAVE THE TAPE SENT
TO THE STATION FOR ANALYSIS.

19:32.291 --> 19:34.041
SERGEANT DOAKES,
YOU'RE ON POINT.

19:34.041 --> 19:35.834
WITH ALL DUE RESPECT, SIR,

19:35.834 --> 19:37.542
LIEUTENANT LaGUERTA'S IN CHARGE
OF THIS INVESTIGATION.

19:37.542 --> 19:39.083
NOT ANYMORE.

19:39.083 --> 19:40.959
THE FACT IS WE HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO CATCH THIS GUY,

19:40.959 --> 19:42.834
AND NOW HE'S RUBBING
OUR NOSES IN IT.

19:42.834 --> 19:45.208
WE'VE GOT TO COME UP
WITH SOME FRESH IDEAS.

19:47.125 --> 19:49.500
THIS IS SOME BULLSHIT.
I'LL GO TALK TO HIM.

19:49.500 --> 19:51.875
NO, NO, NO.
DO AS HE SAYS.

19:51.875 --> 19:54.458
THE COMMISSIONER HAS HIS ASS
IN A SLING.

19:54.458 --> 19:57.667
HE'S UP FOR REVIEW.
WORD IS HE'S GETTING THE BOOT.

19:57.667 --> 20:00.500
SO YOU'RE JUST GONNA SIT BACK
AND TAKE THIS?

20:00.500 --> 20:03.917
WELL, IF IT MEANS BEING SEEN
AS HIS WORTHY SUCCESSOR...

20:03.917 --> 20:05.375
I'LL BE AT THE HOSPITAL.

20:05.375 --> 20:07.166
ALL RIGHT,
P.B. AND J. INSIDE,

20:07.166 --> 20:09.667
CUT DIAGONALLY,
NOT STRAIGHT ACROSS.

20:09.667 --> 20:11.375
TASTES BETTER THAT WAY.

20:11.375 --> 20:14.208
HAS DAD SAID IF HE'S COMING OVER
CHRISTMAS EVE

20:14.208 --> 20:16.750
OR CHRISTMAS MORNING?

20:16.750 --> 20:18.375
I MISS HIM.

20:18.375 --> 20:20.625
WELL, I'M -- I'M AFRAID
YOUR DAD'S NOT GONNA MAKE IT

20:20.625 --> 20:22.125
THIS YEAR FOR THE HOLIDAYS.

20:22.125 --> 20:24.709
WHERE IS HE?

20:24.709 --> 20:26.500
WELL, UH...HE'S --

20:26.500 --> 20:29.083
HE'S BACK IN JAIL,
ISN'T HE?

20:29.083 --> 20:30.375
[ SIGHS ]

20:30.375 --> 20:32.750
LOOK, I KNOW HE WANTED
TO SAY GOODBYE,

20:32.750 --> 20:34.458
BUT THERE WASN'T ANY TIME.

20:34.458 --> 20:36.875
HE LOVES YOU GUYS SO MUCH.

20:36.875 --> 20:39.375
I FORGOT MY MATH BOOK.

20:40.875 --> 20:43.750
I'M -- I'M SURE HE'D LOVE
TO HEAR FROM YOU.

20:43.750 --> 20:45.125
WE COULD WRITE HIM A LETTER.

20:45.125 --> 20:47.166
IT'S ALL YOUR FAULT.

20:47.166 --> 20:49.291
[ SIGHS ]

20:49.291 --> 20:51.875
YOU COULD AT LEAST PRETEND
YOU WANT TO BE HERE.

20:51.875 --> 20:53.417
[ SIGHS ]

20:53.417 --> 20:55.917
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO HAD
THE URGENT NEED FOR TACOS.

20:55.917 --> 20:57.917
YEAH, SO WE COULD TALK
ABOUT RUDY.

20:57.917 --> 20:59.750
HE'S BEEN ACTING
WEIRD LATELY.

20:59.750 --> 21:02.917
LAST NIGHT
HE SAID WE NEED TO TALK.

21:02.917 --> 21:05.208
WELL, THAT'S NEVER GOOD.

21:05.208 --> 21:07.333
WELL, THANKS.
I FEEL A LOT BETTER.

21:07.333 --> 21:09.875
I'VE ONLY BEEN OBSESSING
ABOUT THIS ALL DAY.

21:11.500 --> 21:15.750
THINK YOU COULD TALK TO HIM
FOR ME?

21:15.750 --> 21:17.667
OH, LOOK, IT'S RUDY.

21:17.667 --> 21:19.250
I SORT OF CALLED HIM.

21:19.250 --> 21:21.917
DEX, DEB DIDN'T TELL ME
YOU'D BE JOINING US.

21:21.917 --> 21:23.959
APPARENTLY SHE'S HAD
A LOT ON HER MIND.

21:23.959 --> 21:26.083
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]
OH, SHIT.

21:26.083 --> 21:28.750
THAT'S WORK.
I HAVE TO GO.

21:28.750 --> 21:31.375
HERE, TAKE MINE.
SORRY.

21:37.083 --> 21:39.083
WHAT'S WITH YOUR LIP?

21:39.083 --> 21:41.125
DEB CATCH YOU
WITH A RIGHT HOOK?

21:41.125 --> 21:43.291
SHE CAN BE PRETTY PROTECTIVE
WITH THE REMOTE.

21:43.291 --> 21:46.500
I HAD A LITTLE WORKSHOP ACCIDENT
THIS MORNING.

21:46.500 --> 21:48.792
DOESN'T LOOK LIKE IT HAPPENED
THIS MORNING.

21:48.792 --> 21:50.250
THE CUT'S ALREADY CLOSING UP.

21:50.250 --> 21:51.959
OH, DID I SA--
I MEANT YESTERDAY MORNING.

21:51.959 --> 21:53.917
I THINK I'M WORKING
TOO HARD.

21:53.917 --> 21:56.375
ANYWAY, I DON'T THINK MY LIP

21:56.375 --> 22:00.000
IS WHY DEB ARRANGED
THIS LITTLE CHITCHAT.

22:00.000 --> 22:02.959
MY SISTER IS AFRAID THERE MAY BE
TROUBLE IN PARADISE.

22:02.959 --> 22:05.291
YOUR SISTER'S WRONG.

22:05.291 --> 22:07.583
SO THIS WHOLE
"NEED TO TALK" THING?

22:07.583 --> 22:11.250
I'M STARTING TO LOOK AT
THE BIG PICTURE.

22:11.250 --> 22:13.625
SHE'S SOMEONE
THAT I COULD SEE

22:13.625 --> 22:15.792
SPENDING THE REST
OF MY LIFE WITH, YOU KNOW?

22:15.792 --> 22:19.000
NO, I DON'T KNOW.

22:19.000 --> 22:22.417
BUT I DO KNOW THAT DEB'S
FALLING FOR YOU...HARD.

22:22.417 --> 22:25.000
YOU HURT HER...
AND YOU'LL HURT ME.

22:25.000 --> 22:26.500
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

22:26.500 --> 22:28.166
OOH.

22:28.166 --> 22:30.041
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:31.083 --> 22:34.500
ANGEL, SE RECUPERA.

22:34.500 --> 22:37.417
ANGEL VA A ESTAR EN LA CASA
PARA LA NAVIDAD.

22:37.417 --> 22:40.458
OKAY? EL ES UN HOMBRE
FUERTE Y  STRONG.

22:40.458 --> 22:41.959
Y ADEMáS...

22:41.959 --> 22:44.917
I'M TIRED OF HEARING
YOU TWO GALLINAS  CLUCK.

22:44.917 --> 22:46.875
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:46.875 --> 22:49.709
HEY, YOU.

22:49.709 --> 22:51.834
YOU HAD US SO WORRIED.

22:51.834 --> 22:53.417
IF I'D HAVE KNOWN

22:53.417 --> 22:55.709
THAT THIS WOULD GET YOU BACK
IN THE SAME ROOM WITH ME,

22:55.709 --> 22:58.458
I WOULD HAVE
GOTTEN STABBED SOONER.

22:58.458 --> 23:00.875
I'M GONNA GET THE DOCTOR.

23:06.500 --> 23:08.834
NO, NO, NO.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

23:08.834 --> 23:10.875
NO, DEJALO.

23:10.875 --> 23:13.709
THE DOCTOR SAID YOU'RE
LUCKY TO BE ALIVE AND
STILL HAVE A LIVER.

23:13.709 --> 23:16.041
WELL, THAT'S WHY I GOT TWO,
RIGHT?

23:16.041 --> 23:17.542
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:17.542 --> 23:20.000
IT'S A GOOD THING
YOU DECIDED TO BE A COP.

23:23.291 --> 23:26.041
TELL ME THAT YOU CAUGHT
THE COCKSUCKER

23:26.041 --> 23:28.333
THAT RUINED
ONE OF MY BEST SHIRTS.

23:28.333 --> 23:31.667
WE DON'T HAVE ANY LEADS.
DID YOU SEE ANYTHING?

23:31.667 --> 23:33.667
NO.

23:33.667 --> 23:37.291
HE WAS BEHIND ME.

23:37.291 --> 23:40.834
I JUST FELT THE BLADE GO IN.

23:40.834 --> 23:44.208
IT HAPPENED SO FAST.

23:45.917 --> 23:48.709
MARIA...

23:48.709 --> 23:50.500
HOW LONG HAS NINA BEEN HERE?

23:50.500 --> 23:53.458
SHE WAS THE FIRST ONE
AT THE HOSPITAL.

23:53.458 --> 23:55.583
SHE'S BEEN WITH YOU
THE WHOLE TIME.

23:55.583 --> 23:58.083
YO NO Sé PORQUE, PERO...

23:58.083 --> 23:59.834
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:59.834 --> 24:02.709
[ SNORING ]

24:09.709 --> 24:14.166
Dexter: MY MOTHER WAS MURDERED
BEFORE MY EYES.

24:14.166 --> 24:16.125
MAKES SENSE I'D CHOOSE A LIFE

24:16.125 --> 24:18.750
WHERE I SEARCH FOR MEANING
IN BLOOD.

24:18.750 --> 24:22.792
THE SOLE MEMORY I HAVE OF HER
IS BEING COVERED IN IT.

24:22.792 --> 24:25.250
I NEED TO KNOW MORE DETAILS.

24:29.166 --> 24:32.291
I HOPE THAT LOOK MEANS YOU FOUND
SOMETHING ON BATISTA'S SHIRT.

24:32.291 --> 24:33.834
YOU SHOULD SEE THIS.

24:36.458 --> 24:39.500
THAT'S WHAT I DROVE ALL THE WAY
BACK FROM THE HOSPITAL FOR?

24:39.500 --> 24:42.125
THIS DROP OF BLOOD DOESN'T
MATCH THE WOUND PATTERN

24:42.125 --> 24:44.750
OR THE SPATTER FROM THE REST
OF BATISTA'S SHIRT,

24:44.750 --> 24:47.333
AND LOOK WHERE IT IS -- ON
THE INSIDE OF THE BACK COLLAR.

24:47.333 --> 24:49.792
YOU THINK
IT'S THE ATTACKER'S BLOOD?

24:49.792 --> 24:51.792
WE KNOW
BATISTA FOUGHT BACK.

24:51.792 --> 24:53.458
WELL, RUN THE DNA.

24:53.458 --> 24:55.917
IF THIS GUY'S GOT PRIORS,
WE'LL GET A HIT ON THE DATABASE.

24:55.917 --> 24:58.458
ALREADY SENT A SAMPLE
TO THE LAB.

25:03.166 --> 25:05.583
SORRY TO HEAR, YOU KNOW,

25:05.583 --> 25:07.750
ABOUT MATTHEWS TAKING YOU
OFF THE CASE.

25:07.750 --> 25:10.709
LAST GASP
OF A DESPERATE MAN.

25:10.709 --> 25:14.333
THINGS ARE GONNA CHANGE
AROUND HERE.

25:14.333 --> 25:16.625
AND I WON'T FORGET
YOUR HELP.

25:20.041 --> 25:22.333
[ SIGHS ]

25:22.333 --> 25:25.333
AND I'M VERY, VERY ANGRY.

25:25.333 --> 25:28.041
OH, GOD, NO!
NO, PLEASE!

25:28.041 --> 25:29.792
I CAN'T WATCH THIS AGAIN.

25:29.792 --> 25:33.667
I KNOW IT'S TOUGH, BUT JUST KEEP
YOUR EYES ON THE MONITOR.

25:33.667 --> 25:35.333
WAIT -- WHAT WAS THAT?

25:35.333 --> 25:36.667
THE CAMERA TILTS UP

25:36.667 --> 25:38.750
RIGHT BEFORE HE HITS
THE OFF SWITCH.

25:38.750 --> 25:40.166
WATCH.

25:40.166 --> 25:44.667
THAT, MY FRIENDS, IS A MONSTER
REFRIGERATION UNIT.

25:44.667 --> 25:47.125
HE NEEDS IT COLD
TO PRESERVE THE BODIES.

25:47.125 --> 25:48.375
Masuka:
BUT CHECK THIS OUT.

25:48.375 --> 25:49.834
LOOK HOW MUCH SPACE THERE IS

25:49.834 --> 25:51.875
BETWEEN HER FEET
AND THE CEILING.

25:51.875 --> 25:53.875
THIS ROOM IS BIGGER THAN YOUR
STANDARD COMMERCIAL FREEZER.

25:53.875 --> 25:55.750
MOST LIKELY
IT WAS A CUSTOM BUILD.

25:55.750 --> 25:58.291
SO WE SHOULD FOCUS OUR SEARCH
ON COMMERCIAL DISTRICTS.

25:58.291 --> 26:00.208
NO. RESIDENTIAL.

26:00.208 --> 26:02.208
YOU THINK HE BUILT THIS
IN HIS OWN PLACE?

26:02.208 --> 26:04.625
HE PICKS UP HOOKERS, RIGHT?
I WORKED VICE.

26:04.625 --> 26:06.709
THE SMART GIRLS KNOW NOT TO GO
NEAR A FACTORY OR A WAREHOUSE

26:06.709 --> 26:08.583
UNLESS YOU NEVER
WANT TO BE SEEN AGAIN.

26:08.583 --> 26:11.041
HOW DO WE KNOW HE DIDN'T
KNOCK OUT HIS VICTIMS

26:11.041 --> 26:13.291
OR DRUG THEM, THEN TAKE THEM
BACK TO A WAREHOUSE?

26:13.291 --> 26:15.000
NONE OF THE OTHER VICTIMS
SHOWED ANY SIGNS

26:15.000 --> 26:16.458
OF HEAD INJURY OR NARCOTICS.

26:16.458 --> 26:18.500
BESIDES, WHAT BETTER WAY
TO TRAP A VICTIM

26:18.500 --> 26:20.583
THAN TO GET HER TO WALK
INTO YOUR OWN HOME?

26:20.583 --> 26:22.583
THE ESCORT SERVICE SAID
SHE WAS MEETING HER CLIENT

26:22.583 --> 26:25.000
AT THE CORNER OF BRICKELL AVENUE
AND CORAL WAY.

26:25.000 --> 26:26.875
AND HER BODY WAS FOUND
AT SANTA'S COTTAGE,

26:26.875 --> 26:28.250
WHICH IS ON BISCAYNE MALL.

26:28.250 --> 26:29.417
WE'LL MAP OUT GRIDS.

26:29.417 --> 26:31.583
WE'LL FOCUS ON
PRIVATE RESIDENCES

26:31.583 --> 26:33.709
DRAWING LARGE AMOUNTS OF POWER
NEAR THOSE AREAS.

26:33.709 --> 26:36.208
CATCH A BREAK...

26:36.208 --> 26:37.875
WE'LL CATCH
THIS SON OF A BITCH.

26:39.500 --> 26:41.375
WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU GOING?

26:41.375 --> 26:43.333
I NEED TO DO SOME RESEARCH
ON A CASE.

26:43.333 --> 26:45.542
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO CALL ME
AFTER YOUR LUNCH WITH RUDY.

26:45.542 --> 26:47.458
I'VE BEEN FREAKING OUT.
HE SENT ME THIS TEXT MESSAGE.

26:47.458 --> 26:49.542
"CUM SAIL AWAY WITH ME?"

26:49.542 --> 26:51.417
HE MISSPELLED "COME."

26:51.417 --> 26:53.583
DEXTER,
THIS IS NO TIME TO JOKE.

26:53.583 --> 26:55.834
THIS IS GOOD, RIGHT?
A ROMANTIC WEEKEND?

26:55.834 --> 26:57.625
WHAT DID HE SAY TO YOU?

26:57.625 --> 26:59.041
OH, WAIT, NO.
DON'T.

26:59.041 --> 27:00.250
DON'T TELL ME.

27:00.250 --> 27:01.792
MAYBE HE WANTS IT
TO BE A SURPRISE.

27:01.792 --> 27:04.125
UNLESS I SHOULD KNOW.
SHOULD I KNOW?

27:04.125 --> 27:06.166
OKAY, TELL ME.

27:06.166 --> 27:07.959
YOU KNOW, NO.
DON'T.

27:07.959 --> 27:09.458
"WE NEED TO TALK"?

27:09.458 --> 27:11.041
WHO SAYS THAT UNLESS
YOU'RE GETTING DUMPED?

27:11.041 --> 27:13.125
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

27:13.125 --> 27:15.625
HE PROBABLY WANTS ME OUT ON THE
WATER IN CASE I MAKE A SCENE.

27:15.625 --> 27:17.375
YOU KNOW, I ALWAYS DO THIS.
I PUT MYSELF OUT THERE.

27:17.375 --> 27:18.959
I SET MYSELF UP TO GET HURT.

27:18.959 --> 27:20.625
HE WANTS TO BE
PART OF THE FAMILY.

27:20.625 --> 27:23.375
WHAT?

27:23.375 --> 27:24.709
WAIT.

27:24.709 --> 27:27.083
LIKE...PROPOSE?

27:27.083 --> 27:29.291
I HAVE TO GET TO THE LIBRARY
BEFORE IT CLOSES,

27:29.291 --> 27:32.000
BUT WE'LL TALK
ABOUT THIS LATER, OKAY?

27:32.000 --> 27:34.750
OH, MY GOD.

27:34.750 --> 27:37.041
OH, MY GOD!

27:37.041 --> 27:38.750
AAH!
[ LAUGHING ]

27:45.667 --> 27:48.333
I WAS NEVER ONE
TO DWELL ON MY PAST,

27:48.333 --> 27:50.125
ALWAYS CONTENT
TO LEAVE IT A MYSTERY.

27:50.125 --> 27:51.583
NO DETAILS --

27:51.583 --> 27:54.500
JUST A BLUR OF IMAGES
RUSHING BY.

27:54.500 --> 27:56.083
BUT MY FRIEND OUT THERE

27:56.083 --> 27:59.166
WANTS TO BRING THOSE MEMORIES
INTO FOCUS.

28:03.834 --> 28:05.208
SO DO I.

28:05.208 --> 28:09.583
THIS IS IT FOR THE METRO NEWS
FOR 1972 THROUGH 1973.

28:09.583 --> 28:11.875
THE TRIBUNE'S  ARCHIVES...

28:26.458 --> 28:28.500
10/3?

28:32.375 --> 28:37.125
1-0-3 -- SAME AS THE HOTEL,
SAME AS SANTA'S COTTAGE.

28:37.125 --> 28:40.333
THIS IS WHAT HE WANTED ME
TO FIND ALL ALONG.

28:44.458 --> 28:47.834
DEXTER, CLOSE YOUR EYES.

28:50.291 --> 28:51.959
DON'T LOOK.

28:51.959 --> 28:55.542
LAURA MOSER...

28:55.542 --> 28:57.709
MY MOTHER.

28:57.709 --> 29:01.375
NO WONDER I FELT SO
DISCONNECTED MY ENTIRE LIFE.

29:01.375 --> 29:04.208
IF I DID HAVE EMOTIONS,
I'D HAVE TO FEEL...

29:04.208 --> 29:06.834
THIS.

29:13.250 --> 29:15.667
OCTOBER 3, 1973.

29:15.667 --> 29:17.709
LAURA MOSER
AND THREE OTHERS

29:17.709 --> 29:19.750
FOUND CHOPPED UP
WITH A CHAIN SAW.

29:19.750 --> 29:21.709
APPARENTLY A DRUG DEALER
DIDN'T APPRECIATE

29:21.709 --> 29:23.750
LAURA AND HER FRIENDS
STEALING HIS COCAINE.

29:23.750 --> 29:26.166
FIRST OFFICER ON SCENE
WAS HARRY MORGAN.

29:26.166 --> 29:27.375
YOU'VE BEEN BUSY.

29:27.375 --> 29:28.917
A CRIME THAT BIG

29:28.917 --> 29:30.959
AND YET THERE'S NO RECORD OF
THE CASE FILE AT CITY HALL.

29:30.959 --> 29:32.417
THAT SEEMS A BIT ODD.

29:32.417 --> 29:34.125
IT'S A LONG TIME AGO.

29:34.125 --> 29:37.583
WHAT IS IN THAT REPORT THAT
HARRY DIDN'T WANT ME TO SEE?!

29:37.583 --> 29:40.542
WHY WAS THERE NO MENTION
IN ANY OF THE NEWSPAPERS

29:40.542 --> 29:43.250
ABOUT A 3-YEAR-OLD BOY
AT THE CRIME SCENE?!

29:43.250 --> 29:45.875
CAMILLA...

29:45.875 --> 29:48.417
DAMN IT, I NEED TO KNOW.
I NEED THAT FILE.

29:48.417 --> 29:51.333
I CAN'T GIVE YOU THE FILE
'CAUSE IT NO LONGER EXISTS.

29:51.333 --> 29:54.208
I DESTROYED IT THE DAY
YOUR ADOPTION WENT THROUGH.

29:54.208 --> 29:56.166
YOU DID WHAT?

29:56.166 --> 29:58.709
MADE A PROMISE
TO YOUR FATHER.

29:58.709 --> 30:00.834
WHY, TO PROTECT HIM?

30:03.041 --> 30:04.750
TO PROTECT YOU.

30:12.458 --> 30:13.709
HARRY HAD A CODE.

30:13.709 --> 30:16.458
HE'D NEVER ASK YOU
TO DESTROY EVIDENCE.

30:16.458 --> 30:19.166
YOUR FATHER WAS A DECENT MAN
AND AN HONEST COP,

30:19.166 --> 30:22.125
BUT WHAT HE SAW IN THAT
CARGO CONTAINER CHANGED HIM.

30:22.125 --> 30:25.792
YOU WERE LEFT THERE FOR DAYS,
STARVING,

30:25.792 --> 30:27.625
IN BLOOD 2 INCHES THICK.

30:27.625 --> 30:29.250
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

30:31.291 --> 30:33.458
[ SIGHS ]

30:36.500 --> 30:38.000
YEAH.

30:38.000 --> 30:39.875
DEX, CODY'S RUN AWAY!

30:39.875 --> 30:41.000
ARE YOU SURE?

30:41.000 --> 30:42.750
YEAH, I'VE LOOKED EVERYWHERE.

30:42.750 --> 30:45.875
Well, call the police.
I'll be right there.

30:48.208 --> 30:50.750
CAMILLA...

30:50.750 --> 30:52.792
I NEED TO KNOW THE TRUTH.

30:52.792 --> 30:56.500
KID...

30:56.500 --> 30:58.417
LEAVE THIS ONE ALONE.

30:58.417 --> 31:01.166
Rita: I-I-I CAN'T SIT HERE
LIKE THIS.

31:01.166 --> 31:03.000
I SHOULD BE OUT THERE
DOING SOMETHING.

31:03.000 --> 31:05.125
RITA, THE POLICE SAID
YOU NEED TO STAY HERE

31:05.125 --> 31:06.834
IN CASE CODY COMES HOME.

31:06.834 --> 31:08.917
THE NEIGHBORS ARE HELPING.
WE'LL FIND HIM.

31:08.917 --> 31:12.000
YEAH, BUT ONE SQUAD CAR
FOR ALL OF MIAMI?

31:12.000 --> 31:14.834
WHAT IF SOME CRAZY PERSON
PICKED HIM UP OFF THE STREET?

31:17.667 --> 31:20.709
IT'S ALL MY FAULT.

31:20.709 --> 31:22.959
HONEY, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

31:22.959 --> 31:26.166
I SHOULD HAVE HEARD CODY
GET OUT OF BED.

31:26.166 --> 31:28.583
I'M HIS BIG SISTER.

31:28.583 --> 31:31.250
HEY.
HEY, LOOK AT ME.

31:31.250 --> 31:34.041
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT, OKAY?

31:34.041 --> 31:36.875
OKAY?

31:36.875 --> 31:41.208
COULD YOU GO GET DEXTER
SOME WATER?

31:41.208 --> 31:44.333
[ SIGHS ]

31:44.333 --> 31:46.792
OH, GOD.

31:46.792 --> 31:49.333
I SHOULD HAVE
SEEN THIS COMING.

31:49.333 --> 31:51.000
CODY WAS SO UPSET WITH ME

31:51.000 --> 31:54.125
WHEN I TOLD HIM THAT PAUL
WAS BACK IN JAIL.

31:54.125 --> 31:55.792
PAUL.

31:55.792 --> 31:57.542
TODAY'S THURSDAY, RIGHT?

31:57.542 --> 31:59.083
YEAH.

31:59.083 --> 32:02.125
I THINK I KNOW
WHERE CODY MIGHT BE.

32:11.959 --> 32:13.875
HEY.

32:13.875 --> 32:16.041
NEED A PUSH?

32:18.250 --> 32:20.166
HEY.

32:20.166 --> 32:22.917
TODAY'S THE DAY YOU MEET DADDY
IN THE PARK, HUH?

32:22.917 --> 32:24.500
HE'LL BE HERE.

32:24.500 --> 32:27.875
OH, BABY, I'M SO SORRY,
BUT HE'S NOT COMING BACK --

32:27.875 --> 32:29.542
NOT FOR A LONG TIME.

32:32.125 --> 32:35.250
LOOK, WE'LL TALK ABOUT THIS
WHEN WE GET HOME, OKAY?

32:35.250 --> 32:38.750
AFTER ALL THE LIES
HARRY LEFT FOR ME TO UNCOVER,

32:38.750 --> 32:40.834
I'D LOVE TO RUN AWAY, TOO.

32:40.834 --> 32:44.291
[ SIGHS ]
HE WON'T EVEN LOOK AT ME.

32:44.291 --> 32:48.625
I'M NOT THE ONE IN JAIL,
AND YET I'M STILL THE BAD GUY.

32:48.625 --> 32:51.291
WELL, YOU DIDN'T TELL THEM
THE TRUTH...

32:51.291 --> 32:52.917
ABOUT THEIR FATHER.

32:52.917 --> 32:55.250
I TOLD THEM
PAUL WAS BACK IN JAIL.

32:55.250 --> 32:57.458
WELL, RIGHT, YOU TOLD THEM
WHERE  HE IS,

32:57.458 --> 32:59.208
BUT YOU DIDN'T TELL THEM
WHO  HE IS.

32:59.208 --> 33:01.750
HE'S STILL
THE SAME DRUG-USING,

33:01.750 --> 33:04.500
WIFE-BEATING REDNECK
HE ALWAYS WAS.

33:04.500 --> 33:06.125
THEY SHOULD HEAR THAT.

33:06.125 --> 33:08.959
YOU'RE NOT A PARENT.
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

33:08.959 --> 33:10.959
YOU DO ANYTHING
TO PROTECT YOUR KIDS.

33:10.959 --> 33:13.208
RITA, WAKE UP.
YOU'RE NOT PROTECTING THEM.

33:13.208 --> 33:15.959
YOU'RE PROTECTING PAUL.

33:15.959 --> 33:18.917
WELL, I --
I GOT TO GET THEM HOME.

33:28.959 --> 33:31.041
[ HUMMING ]

33:32.875 --> 33:35.291
SOMEBODY'S
IN A GOOD MOOD.

33:35.291 --> 33:37.208
THE COMMISSIONER
AND THE REVIEW BOARD

33:37.208 --> 33:39.542
DID NOT LOOK HAPPY
THIS MORNING.

33:39.542 --> 33:41.834
THEY'VE BEEN IN MATTHEWS' OFFICE
FOR TWO HOURS.

33:41.834 --> 33:44.000
YOU THINKING HIS ASS IS ABOUT
THREE SHADES OF RED RIGHT NOW?

33:44.000 --> 33:45.917
I DON'T CARE
WHAT COLOR IT IS

33:45.917 --> 33:47.834
AS LONG AS IT'S ON ITS WAY
OUT THE DOOR.

33:47.834 --> 33:50.583
[ LAUGHTER ]

33:50.583 --> 33:52.542
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

33:57.792 --> 34:00.041
TELL ME THAT DID NOT
JUST HAPPEN.

34:00.041 --> 34:02.250
IT'S WHO YOU KNOW
AND WHO YOU BLOW.

34:02.250 --> 34:04.750
PROBABLY PICKING
THEIR FUCKING TEE TIME.

34:04.750 --> 34:06.792
MARIA, WATCH YOUR BACK.

34:06.792 --> 34:09.875
HE'S GONNA BE GUNNING FOR YOU
NOW MORE THAN EVER.

34:09.875 --> 34:12.166
LET HIM TRY.

34:16.792 --> 34:19.208
Angel:
MY MAN JUAN, HOOK IT UP.

34:19.208 --> 34:22.041
THEY DIDN'T HAVE
ROAD AND TRACK  SO...

34:23.750 --> 34:26.291
THAT BETTER BE
A BAG OF APPLESAUCE.

34:26.291 --> 34:28.667
OKAY, JUAN, AT THIS POINT,
YOU SHOULD GO SAVE YOURSELF.

34:28.667 --> 34:30.709
GO.

34:30.709 --> 34:33.667
OH, YOU GOT TO BE
KIDDING ME.

34:33.667 --> 34:35.709
TWO DOUBLE-MEATS?

34:35.709 --> 34:37.041
A MAN'S GOT TO EAT.

34:39.000 --> 34:40.875
YOU'RE SO CUTE
WHEN YOU'RE ANNOYED.

34:40.875 --> 34:43.208
YOU KNOW, YOUR MOUTH MAKES
THOSE LITTLE O's.

34:43.208 --> 34:44.834
GOD DAMN IT, ANGEL,

34:44.834 --> 34:46.750
DO I LOOK LIKE I'M BEING
FUCKING CUTE WITH YOU?

34:46.750 --> 34:48.583
WELL,
NOT NOW YOU DON'T, NO.

34:48.583 --> 34:50.583
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS DO THIS --

34:50.583 --> 34:52.834
MAKE LIGHT OF THINGS
THAT MATTER?

34:52.834 --> 34:55.875
OKAY, I'M SORRY.
OKAY?

34:55.875 --> 34:58.959
WHEN I COME HOME,
I'LL EAT ANYTHING YOU WANT.

34:58.959 --> 35:02.583
NO JOKES, NO COMPLAINING --
I PROMISE.

35:02.583 --> 35:04.208
WHEN YOU COME HOME?

35:05.875 --> 35:09.417
I THOUGHT THE WAY THINGS
ARE GOING WITH US...

35:09.417 --> 35:11.792
I THOUGHT
YOU'D FORGIVEN ME.

35:13.959 --> 35:16.917
WELL, OF COURSE
I FORGIVE YOU.

35:16.917 --> 35:20.250
I FORGAVE YOU
A LONG TIME AGO.

35:20.250 --> 35:23.041
OKAY, SO LET'S FIX THIS.

35:23.041 --> 35:25.291
THIS COULD BE
A SECOND CHANCE FOR US.

35:27.291 --> 35:29.333
WHAT?
[ SIGHS ]

35:31.542 --> 35:36.083
LOOK,
YOU DID WHAT YOU DID.

35:36.083 --> 35:39.000
IT WAS HARD.

35:39.000 --> 35:43.583
BUT IT GOT US
TO FACE THE TRUTH.

35:43.583 --> 35:48.125
WE WERE MISERABLE...
FOR YEARS.

35:48.125 --> 35:50.125
DO YOU REALLY
WANT TO SURVIVE THIS

35:50.125 --> 35:52.500
AND GO RIGHT BACK
TO BEING UNHAPPY?

35:52.500 --> 35:53.625
MAYBE.

35:53.625 --> 35:56.458
WHAT IF I DO?

35:59.750 --> 36:03.041
LOOK, YOU WILL ALWAYS BE
JORGE'S FATHER.

36:03.041 --> 36:06.417
I WILL ALWAYS
CARE ABOUT YOU.

36:08.917 --> 36:11.625
I'LL ALWAYS BE HERE
FOR YOU.

36:13.333 --> 36:16.834
BUT OUR MARRIAGE IS OVER.

36:27.667 --> 36:29.333
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

36:29.333 --> 36:32.834
WHY, YES, BY ALL MEANS, TOM,
PLEASE, COME IN.

36:32.834 --> 36:36.458
MARIA...
LET'S YOU AND ME HAVE A TALK.

36:36.458 --> 36:39.333
CONGRATULATIONS ON THE REVIEW.
I HEAR IT WENT WELL.

36:39.333 --> 36:42.125
YOU MUST BE THRILLED.
BUT NOW, IF YOU DON'T MIND --

36:42.125 --> 36:43.750
LET ME GET
RIGHT TO THE POINT.

36:43.750 --> 36:46.125
ALL OUR MISHAPS
THESE LAST FEW MONTHS --

36:46.125 --> 36:48.834
FAILURE TO BRING
IN THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER,

36:48.834 --> 36:51.125
MISHANDLING OF TONY TUCCI...

36:51.125 --> 36:52.709
EVEN NEIL PERRY --

36:52.709 --> 36:56.417
NEIL PERRY WAS YOUR FUCK-UP...
NOT MINE.

36:56.417 --> 36:59.250
THEY'RE ALL THE RESULT
OF A BAD COMMAND STRUCTURE,

36:59.250 --> 37:01.250
AND THAT'S MY FAILURE.

37:03.166 --> 37:04.834
WELL...

37:04.834 --> 37:08.291
I'M GLAD TO HEAR YOU
SAY THAT.

37:08.291 --> 37:11.792
TAKES A BIG MAN TO ADMIT
HIS OWN MISTAKES.

37:11.792 --> 37:14.208
SO THIS MORNING,

37:14.208 --> 37:16.709
THE COMMISSIONER
GAVE ME THE GO-AHEAD

37:16.709 --> 37:18.583
TO RESTRUCTURE THE DIVISION.

37:18.583 --> 37:20.166
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY,

37:20.166 --> 37:23.041
YOU WILL NO LONGER SERVE
AS MY LIEUTENANT.

37:23.041 --> 37:25.208
I'M SORRY.

37:25.208 --> 37:27.542
I KNOW THIS MUST BE DIFFICULT
FOR YOU.

37:27.542 --> 37:31.083
[ CHUCKLES ]
PLEASE, IT'S RIDICULOUS.

37:33.417 --> 37:35.500
YOU REALLY
DON'T WANT TO DO THIS.

37:35.500 --> 37:39.125
BECAUSE OF YOUR STATUS
IN THE CUBAN COMMUNITY.

37:39.125 --> 37:40.750
I'M A FUCKING HERO
TO THIS COMMUNITY.

37:40.750 --> 37:42.583
YOU THINK THEY'RE JUST GONNA
ACCEPT IT?

37:42.583 --> 37:44.417
YOUR REPLACEMENT HAS ALREADY
BEEN SELECTED.

37:44.417 --> 37:47.375
HER NAME IS ESMé PASCAL, A
TRANSFER FROM FORT LAUDERDALE --

37:47.375 --> 37:48.792
A REAL UP-AND-COMER.

37:48.792 --> 37:52.250
PASCAL,
THE HAITIAN-AMERICAN?

37:52.250 --> 37:55.333
THE ONE WHO GOT SHOT LAST YEAR
IN THE LINE OF DUTY.

37:55.333 --> 37:58.667
MM-HMM.
TURNS OUT SHE'S AN ACTUAL  HERO.

37:58.667 --> 38:00.417
YOU THINK I'M GONNA
STAY QUIET FOR THIS,

38:00.417 --> 38:01.542
YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR MIND.

38:01.542 --> 38:03.375
I DID WARN YOU, MARIA.

38:04.959 --> 38:08.625
I'M GONNA NEED YOU TO CLEAR OUT
THIS OFFICE TONIGHT.

38:08.625 --> 38:10.583
EXPECT A CALL
FROM MY UNION REP.

38:10.583 --> 38:13.083
YOU'LL ALWAYS HAVE A PLACE
IN THE BULLPEN --

38:13.083 --> 38:14.458
AND MY FUCKING LAWYER, TOO!

38:14.458 --> 38:16.250
...WITH ALL THE OTHER
DETECTIVES.

38:16.250 --> 38:17.792
THIS ISN'T FUCKING OVER, TOM!

38:17.792 --> 38:20.834
YOU GODDAMN...
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

38:20.834 --> 38:22.417
SON OF A BITCH!

38:29.166 --> 38:31.458
OH, YOU GOT TO BE
KIDDING ME.

38:31.458 --> 38:32.458
HOW ARE YOU?

38:32.458 --> 38:34.041
[ SIGHS ]

38:34.041 --> 38:35.792
HOW THE HELL DO I LOOK?

38:35.792 --> 38:38.875
I CAN BARELY REMEMBER
HOW I GOT HERE.

38:38.875 --> 38:41.000
LOOK, THERE'S SOMETHING
WE NEED TO DISCUSS.

38:41.000 --> 38:43.375
IF YOU CAME FOR AN APOLOGY,
YOU WASTED A TANK OF GAS.

38:43.375 --> 38:45.333
SIT.
I'M NOT FINISHED.

38:45.333 --> 38:46.500
FUCK YOU.

38:46.500 --> 38:49.500
ASTOR AND CODY
ARE IN THE OTHER ROOM.

38:52.625 --> 38:54.458
JESUS,
YOU BROUGHT THEM HERE?

38:54.458 --> 38:57.291
LOOK, I KNOW
THIS WILL BE DIFFICULT,

38:57.291 --> 38:59.875
BUT I NEED YOU TO EXPLAIN TO
THEM WHY YOU'RE IN THIS PLACE.

38:59.875 --> 39:03.125
I HAVE NO FUCKING IDEA
WHY I'M IN THIS PLACE.

39:03.125 --> 39:06.000
[ SCOFFS ]
FINE. FINE.

39:06.000 --> 39:08.208
YOU WANT TO BE IN DENIAL?
GO AHEAD.

39:08.208 --> 39:10.458
YOU WILL NEVER SEE
YOUR KIDS AGAIN.

39:10.458 --> 39:13.375
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
RITA, WAIT, WAIT.

39:15.542 --> 39:18.000
I FOUGHT SO HARD
TO WIN THOSE KIDS BACK,

39:18.000 --> 39:19.834
ESPECIALLY ASTOR.

39:19.834 --> 39:22.959
IF THEY SEE ME HERE LIKE THIS,
I'M GONNA LOSE THEM FOREVER.

39:22.959 --> 39:25.959
PAUL, THE ONE GOOD THING
THAT CAME OUT OF OUR MARRIAGE

39:25.959 --> 39:27.375
ARE THOSE KIDS.

39:27.375 --> 39:29.583
AND I KNOW YOU LOVE THEM.

39:29.583 --> 39:31.458
BUT IF YOU WANT TO HAVE

39:31.458 --> 39:33.375
ANY KIND OF REAL
RELATIONSHIP WITH THEM,

39:33.375 --> 39:35.750
IT HAS TO BE
WITH THE FATHER THEY HAVE,

39:35.750 --> 39:39.000
NOT THE FATHER
THEY WISH  THEY HAD.

39:39.000 --> 39:41.125
NOW, YOU CHEATED ON ME.

39:41.125 --> 39:43.583
YOU BROKE MY HEART,
YOU BROKE MY BONES,

39:43.583 --> 39:47.333
AND I TOOK IT SO THOSE KIDS
WOULDN'T HAVE TO.

39:47.333 --> 39:51.583
BUT I AM GIVING YOU THE CHANCE
TO MAKE IT ALL RIGHT.

39:51.583 --> 39:54.625
NOT FOR ME,
BUT FOR THEM.

39:54.625 --> 39:58.375
I-I-I...I WOULDN'T KNOW
WHAT TO SAY.

39:58.375 --> 40:04.000
TELL THEM YOU'RE PAYING
FOR YOUR MISTAKES.

40:04.000 --> 40:06.250
IT'S A VALUABLE LESSON.

40:06.250 --> 40:08.417
IT'S ONE YOU NEVER GOT.

40:11.583 --> 40:14.333
SO WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?

40:19.041 --> 40:21.375
OKAY.

40:23.083 --> 40:25.083
Cody: DADDY!
DADDY, DADDY!

40:25.083 --> 40:28.208
HEY!
[ CHUCKLING ]

40:38.917 --> 40:40.834
ALL RIGHT,
THIS WON'T TAKE LONG.

40:40.834 --> 40:42.458
THERE WAS A DROP OF BLOOD

40:42.458 --> 40:44.917
ON THE BACK OF YOUR SHIRT
THAT WASN'T YOURS,

40:44.917 --> 40:47.208
SO I NEED TO CHECK
THE BACK OF YOUR HEAD.

40:47.208 --> 40:49.166
JUST SO LONG
AS IT'S ONLY MY HEAD

40:49.166 --> 40:51.083
YOU'RE CHECKING
BACK THERE, BRO.

40:51.083 --> 40:53.041
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:53.041 --> 40:55.750
HOW ARE THINGS
WITH YOU AND RITA?

40:55.750 --> 41:00.250
NOT SO GOOD, ACTUALLY.
WE KIND OF...HAD WORDS.

41:00.250 --> 41:01.917
I THINK I REALLY UPSET HER.

41:01.917 --> 41:03.291
OH, THAT'S ROUGH, MAN.

41:03.291 --> 41:06.417
MAYBE I'M NOT
THE RIGHT PERSON FOR HER.

41:06.417 --> 41:08.417
SOME PEOPLE ARE MEANT TO BE
ALONE, RIGHT?

41:08.417 --> 41:11.333
DEX, SOCIO,  ALONE SUCKS.

41:11.333 --> 41:13.500
iHIJO DE PUTA!
SORRY.

41:13.500 --> 41:16.542
THESE ARE TEETH MARKS.

41:16.542 --> 41:19.834
YOU DEFINITELY
WOUNDED THIS GUY.

41:19.834 --> 41:21.083
GOOD.

41:21.083 --> 41:23.333
I HOPE I BROKE
HIS FUCKING NOSE...

41:23.333 --> 41:25.583
OR AT LEAST GAVE HIM
A FAT LIP.

41:27.625 --> 41:31.458
ANGEL, HAVE YOU EVER MET
DEB'S BOYFRIEND, RUDY COOPER?

41:31.458 --> 41:34.875
YEAH. I WENT BY HIS OFFICE
A COUPLE OF DAYS AGO.

41:34.875 --> 41:37.083
NICE GUY. WHY?

41:41.667 --> 41:44.583
AT LUNCH, RUDY SAID HE'D HURT
HIS LIP THAT MORNING.

41:44.583 --> 41:48.166
HE WAS LYING, AND I WAS
TOO DISTRACTED TO CARE.

41:48.166 --> 41:50.208
BUT HE'S GOT
MY FULL ATTENTION NOW.

41:50.208 --> 41:52.125
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

41:58.542 --> 42:00.500
HEY, YOU HERE TONIGHT?

42:00.500 --> 42:02.750
YEAH, WE'RE TITS-DEEP
IN THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

42:02.750 --> 42:05.208
MIGHT BE ONTO SOMETHING.
IT'S GONNA BE AN ALL-NIGHTER.

42:05.208 --> 42:07.208
SO THAT TEXT MESSAGE
YOU GOT FROM RUDY

42:07.208 --> 42:10.041
ABOUT GOING AWAY WITH HIM --
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DO THAT?

42:10.041 --> 42:11.667
TRAGICALLY, NO.

42:11.667 --> 42:14.375
I WAS ALL PSYCHED TO MEET HIM
AT THE MIAMI BEACH MARINA,

42:14.375 --> 42:16.834
BUT THIS BULLPEN'S MY HOME
TILL WE FINISH THIS.

42:16.834 --> 42:18.542
GOOD.

42:18.542 --> 42:20.750
I'M WORKING ON A THEORY
THAT RUDY WAS GONNA PROPOSE,

42:20.750 --> 42:22.667
AND NOW HE CAN'T --
WHY IS THAT GOOD?

42:22.667 --> 42:24.834
NO, I MEANT GOOD THAT
YOU'RE MAKING PROGRESS HERE.

42:24.834 --> 42:26.709
YEAH.
WE'RE GETTING CLOSER.

42:26.709 --> 42:28.166
FINGERS CROSSED.

42:28.166 --> 42:30.250
AT LEAST I KNOW MY SISTER
IS SAFE TONIGHT,

42:30.250 --> 42:33.250
WHICH GIVES ME TIME TO CHECK
OUT MY OWN THEORY ON RUDY.

42:33.250 --> 42:36.625
WE'VE DEFINED THE AREA
FOR THE RESIDENTIAL SEARCH.

42:36.625 --> 42:38.625
GOOD. SO WE'LL START
CANVASSING TONIGHT.

42:38.625 --> 42:40.750
YOU TAKE THE --
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

42:45.083 --> 42:46.792
THAT HIM?

42:46.792 --> 42:48.750
YEAH, HOW'D YOU KNOW?

42:48.750 --> 42:52.542
'CAUSE YOU GOT THAT STUPID-ASS
GRIN ON YOUR FACE AGAIN.

42:52.542 --> 42:54.750
GO AHEAD.
ANSWER IT.
OKAY.

42:56.959 --> 42:58.500
HEY.

42:58.500 --> 43:00.959
Rudy: Hey, supercop,
what's the word?

43:00.959 --> 43:02.750
I'M KIND OF IN A THING
RIGHT NOW.

43:02.750 --> 43:05.667
GOT IT. I'LL BE QUICK.
YOU NEVER ANSWERED MY TEXT.

43:05.667 --> 43:08.208
DO I HAVE THE PLEASURE
OF YOUR COMPANY THIS WEEKEND?

43:08.208 --> 43:10.417
UH, YEAH, ABOUT THAT --

43:10.417 --> 43:12.333
COME ON, DEB,
IT'S ONLY TWO DAYS.

43:12.333 --> 43:13.583
I KNOW, I KNOW.

43:13.583 --> 43:15.417
IT'S JUST WE'VE HAD
A MAJOR BREAK

43:15.417 --> 43:17.166
IN THE ICE-TRUCK-KILLER CASE.

43:17.166 --> 43:19.750
I PROMISE, AS SOON AS WE CATCH
THIS DOUCHEBAG,

43:19.750 --> 43:22.625
YOU AND I ARE GONNA SPEND
A WHOLE WEEK TOGETHER IN BED.

43:22.625 --> 43:25.417
You are not gonna be able
to get rid of me.

43:25.417 --> 43:28.083
OKAY, OKAY,
BUT HOW ABOUT DINNER?

43:28.083 --> 43:30.375
Oh, my God,
you are persistent.

43:30.375 --> 43:32.000
WELL, YOU GOT TO EAT, RIGHT?

43:32.000 --> 43:34.917
SO WHY NOT
EAT DINNER WITH ME...

43:34.917 --> 43:37.083
ON THIS YACHT I'M ON?

43:37.083 --> 43:38.959
WHERE THE HELL
DID YOU GET A YACHT?

43:38.959 --> 43:40.583
I RENTED IT.

43:40.583 --> 43:42.750
I THOUGHT WE'D HAVE
A NICE COUPLE DAYS TOGETHER,

43:42.750 --> 43:45.083
BUT WE COULD STILL HAVE
A NICE NIGHT.

43:45.083 --> 43:47.875
AND THERE IS THAT THING
WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT.

43:47.875 --> 43:49.792
UM...

43:49.792 --> 43:52.208
OKAY, WELL, MAYBE I CAN TAKE
AN HOUR FOR DINNER.

43:52.208 --> 43:54.291
I CAN WORK WITH AN HOUR.

43:54.291 --> 43:56.083
I mean, a real hour,
not one of your

43:56.083 --> 43:58.041
"LET'S STRETCH THIS OUT
TILL 2:00 A.M.

43:58.041 --> 44:00.125
YOU MIGHT AS WELL STAY
AND HAVE SEX" HOURS.

44:00.125 --> 44:01.291
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

44:01.291 --> 44:03.291
Right. Real hour.

44:03.291 --> 44:05.875
NO FAKEY HOUR.
GOT IT.

44:05.875 --> 44:08.125
ALL RIGHT, I'LL GET OUT OF HERE
AS FAST AS I CAN.

44:08.125 --> 44:10.625
I'LL SEE YOU SOON.

44:16.834 --> 44:20.208
THINKING RUDY ATTACKED BATISTA
DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

44:20.208 --> 44:21.792
HE'S A LOVING BOYFRIEND.

44:21.792 --> 44:23.583
HE SPENDS HIS LIFE
HELPING PEOPLE IN NEED.

44:23.583 --> 44:25.500
HE BROUGHT ME STEAKS.

44:27.709 --> 44:29.709
WELL, THAT'S JUST RUDE.

44:29.709 --> 44:32.125
WHY WOULD LOVING
AND HELPFUL RUDY

44:32.125 --> 44:35.125
NEED AN INDUSTRIAL-GRADE
LOCK...

44:35.125 --> 44:37.458
AND A SECURITY CAMERA?

44:37.458 --> 44:40.667
HOW DO I GET HIS DNA NOW?

44:51.333 --> 44:53.166
[ RUSTLING ]

44:59.583 --> 45:01.542
AT TIMES LIKE THIS,

45:01.542 --> 45:05.166
I WISH THE TRUTH WAS MORE
EASILY ACCESSIBLE, UNLESS --

45:05.166 --> 45:08.667
RIGHT.

45:08.667 --> 45:11.000
BUT HARRY TAUGHT ME
TO TRUST MY GUT.

45:11.000 --> 45:13.834
"PEOPLE LIE ALL THE TIME,"
HE SAID.

45:13.834 --> 45:17.709
"BUT YOUR INSTINCT
WILL NEVER FAIL YOU."

45:17.709 --> 45:19.417
HMM.

45:19.417 --> 45:22.333
SOME BLOOD FROM A CUT LIP,
PERHAPS?

45:30.208 --> 45:32.917
FUCK ME!

45:32.917 --> 45:35.917
I BELIEVE YOUR RULE SPECIFICALLY
PROHIBITS SUCH ACTION.

45:40.208 --> 45:41.875
[ GIGGLES ]

45:41.875 --> 45:43.500
DID YOU DO ALL THIS?

45:43.500 --> 45:46.875
IN FACT, I DID.

45:46.875 --> 45:48.500
YOU LIKE?

45:48.500 --> 45:49.834
I LIKE.

45:49.834 --> 45:51.542
I LIKE SO MUCH

45:51.542 --> 45:54.000
THAT IT MAKES WHAT I HAVE
TO TELL YOU THAT MUCH HARDER.

45:54.000 --> 45:55.917
OH, PLEASE TELL ME
YOU'RE NOT LEAVING.

45:55.917 --> 45:57.375
I'M SORRY. I HIT TRAFFIC.

45:57.375 --> 45:59.125
IT TOOK ME 30 MINUTES
TO GET HERE.

45:59.125 --> 46:01.250
I HAVE TO TURN AROUND
AND GO RIGHT BACK.

46:01.250 --> 46:03.375
OH, MY GOD.

46:03.375 --> 46:05.542
HOLD ON. HOLD ON.
WAIT.

46:05.542 --> 46:07.750
WELL, YOU'RE SORT OF
FORCING MY HAND HERE.

46:07.750 --> 46:10.417
I WANTED TO WAIT UNTIL WE WERE
OUT IN THE WATER, BUT...

46:10.417 --> 46:13.542
[ SIGHS ] HERE GOES.

46:13.542 --> 46:16.417
I KNOW THIS SEEMS FAST...

46:16.417 --> 46:17.917
BUT I FEEL --

46:17.917 --> 46:20.917
I FEEL THAT I WAITED MY WHOLE
ENTIRE LIFE FOR YOU.

46:20.917 --> 46:24.542
AND NOW THAT YOU'RE HERE,

46:24.542 --> 46:26.750
I DON'T WANT YOU TO LEAVE.

46:26.750 --> 46:30.041
DEBRA MORGAN...

46:30.041 --> 46:31.750
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

46:31.750 --> 46:33.041
[ LAUGHING ]

46:33.041 --> 46:35.000
I KNEW IT!
I FUCKING KNEW IT!

46:35.000 --> 46:36.959
IS THAT YOUR VERSION
OF A "YES"?

46:36.959 --> 46:39.542
YES, YES, YES, YES,
BUT --

46:39.542 --> 46:41.375
NO, NO, NO!
STOP AT "YES."

46:41.375 --> 46:43.208
YES, I LIKE THAT PART.

46:43.208 --> 46:45.792
YES, BUT LET'S SLOW IT DOWN,
YOU KNOW?

46:45.792 --> 46:48.750
LIKE, LET ME SAVOR THIS.
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

46:48.750 --> 46:50.375
I WANT TO ENJOY IT,
YOU KNOW?

46:50.375 --> 46:52.625
SO IT'S A "YES," BUT --

46:52.625 --> 46:54.542
OKAY, I GET IT.
YOU DO?

46:54.542 --> 46:57.125
NO, NOT REALLY,
BUT I CAN WORK WITH IT.

46:57.125 --> 46:58.792
GOOD, GOOD.

46:58.792 --> 47:01.417
OH, GOD, I CAN STILL WEAR
THE RING, RIGHT?

47:01.417 --> 47:04.166
YES, BUT...
THERE'S A CONDITION.

47:04.166 --> 47:07.792
I KNOW YOU HAVE TO
GO TO WORK, BUT...

47:07.792 --> 47:10.291
IF YOU'RE GONNA WEAR THE RING,
WE NEED TO CELEBRATE.

47:10.291 --> 47:13.125
ONE GLASS OF CHAMPAGNE --
THAT'S ALL I ASK.

47:13.125 --> 47:14.959
RUDY, I --
I MEAN IT.

47:14.959 --> 47:17.208
YOU CAN'T LEAVE YOUR
SORT-OF FIANCé ON A YACHT

47:17.208 --> 47:19.500
WITH A COLD MEAL AND AN UNOPENED
BOTTLE OF CHAMPAGNE.

47:19.500 --> 47:20.959
IT'S KIND OF CRUEL.

47:20.959 --> 47:24.709
JUST ONE GLASS OF CHAMPAGNE...
TO CELEBRATE.

47:24.709 --> 47:26.750
AND THEN YOU CAN GO BACK,

47:26.750 --> 47:29.208
SAVING MIAMI
FROM THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

47:29.208 --> 47:31.709
I CAN LIVE WITH THAT.

47:36.500 --> 47:38.959
HEY, I NEED THESE TWO
TESTED AGAINST EACH OTHER.

47:38.959 --> 47:41.000
IT'S KIND OF A RUSH.

47:41.000 --> 47:42.250
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

47:42.250 --> 47:44.166
EXCUSE ME, HI.

47:44.166 --> 47:46.083
[ SIGHS ]

47:46.083 --> 47:49.333
HEY, THESE TWO -- TESTED AGAINST
EACH OTHER RIGHT NOW.

47:49.333 --> 47:50.709
OKAY.

47:55.166 --> 47:57.583
Debra: It's Deb. Do it.

47:57.583 --> 47:59.458
HEY, I KNOW YOU'RE WORKING,

47:59.458 --> 48:01.417
BUT LET ME KNOW
WHEN YOU COME UP FOR AIR.

48:01.417 --> 48:04.208
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.
I'M IN THE BUILDING.

48:08.417 --> 48:10.583
[ CHUCKLES ]

48:10.583 --> 48:12.500
THIS YACHT'S AMAZING.

48:12.500 --> 48:15.000
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WENT
FOR STUFF LIKE THIS.

48:15.000 --> 48:17.750
WELL, YOU HAVE A WHOLE LOT
TO LEARN ABOUT ME.

48:17.750 --> 48:19.834
WAS THAT JUST
THE PHONE RINGING?

48:19.834 --> 48:22.291
YEAH -- BIG BROTHER.
I LET IT GO TO VOICE MAIL.

48:22.291 --> 48:24.125
HE CAN WAIT
TILL WE'RE DONE HERE.

48:24.125 --> 48:27.834
GOOD.
I WANT YOU ALL TO MYSELF.

48:27.834 --> 48:30.625
SO...
LET THE TOASTING BEGIN.

48:30.625 --> 48:35.500
TO...WHAT COMES NEXT.

48:38.792 --> 48:41.083
MMM.

48:41.083 --> 48:43.125
YOU'RE NOT DRINKING.

48:47.083 --> 48:48.875
[ CHUCKLES ]

48:48.875 --> 48:51.250
TASTES LIKE MENTHOL,

48:51.250 --> 48:54.250
WHICH, IT TURNS OUT,
IS NOT THAT SEXY.

48:59.000 --> 49:00.583
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

49:00.583 --> 49:02.625
NOTHING.

49:04.583 --> 49:07.750
JUST BAD MEMORIES.

49:07.750 --> 49:10.417
OH.
THAT'S RIGHT.

49:10.417 --> 49:12.250
THAT WAS THE --

49:12.250 --> 49:15.625
THE ONE CLUE THE ICE-TRUCK
KILLER LEFT BEHIND, RIGHT?

49:15.625 --> 49:18.750
RIGHT.

49:18.750 --> 49:21.208
WAIT.
HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT?

49:21.208 --> 49:23.625
I DON'T OFTEN MAKE MISTAKES,

49:23.625 --> 49:28.125
BUT WHEN I DO,
THEY HAUNT ME.

49:28.125 --> 49:31.458
HILARIOUS.

49:31.458 --> 49:33.750
YOUR CHAMPAGNE'S
GONNA GET WARM.

49:33.750 --> 49:37.250
YOU KNOW THE ONE THING
I'VE BEEN DYING TO ASK YOU?

49:37.250 --> 49:40.375
HOW DID YOU NOT KNOW
WHO I WAS?

49:40.375 --> 49:42.750
YOU'RE A COP.

49:45.458 --> 49:47.792
THIS ISN'T FUNNY.

49:47.792 --> 49:50.458
I THINK
A REAL COP WOULD, UM,

49:50.458 --> 49:52.875
AT LEAST HAVE A SENSE
THAT SHE WAS IN THE PRESENCE

49:52.875 --> 49:55.959
OF THE PERSON
SHE WAS HUNTING, RIGHT?

49:55.959 --> 49:58.792
YOU'RE HURTING ME.

49:58.792 --> 50:01.208
I'M DIDN'T SHOW YOU
THE BEST PART OF MY LOFT.

50:01.208 --> 50:04.000
BUILT IT MYSELF.

50:04.000 --> 50:05.333
STOP IT!

50:05.333 --> 50:07.458
THE REFRIGERATED ROOM.

50:09.333 --> 50:11.333
OH, GOD,
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?!

50:11.333 --> 50:13.750
YOU KNOW, THE TRICKY PART
WAS GETTING YOU ON THE BOAT.

50:13.750 --> 50:15.000
AAH!

50:15.000 --> 50:17.041
THE OTHER WOMEN
I COULD JUST PAY.

50:17.041 --> 50:21.750
BUT AT THE END...
YOU MADE IT EASY.

50:21.750 --> 50:25.166
SO DESPERATE
TO FALL IN LOVE.

50:28.291 --> 50:30.041
STOP.

50:43.166 --> 50:46.709
DUDE, YOU GOT TO SEE THIS.

50:46.709 --> 50:48.875
THE AUTOPSY ON OUR
SANTA'S COTTAGE VICTIM?

50:48.875 --> 50:50.583
CHECK IT OUT.

50:50.583 --> 50:53.542
ONE ARM WAS SHORTER
THAN THE OTHER.

50:53.542 --> 50:55.208
SO THAT GOT ME THINKING.

50:55.208 --> 50:58.667
I MEAN, OUR GUY ISN'T SLOPPY.
HE'S PRECISE.

50:58.667 --> 51:00.250
NOT NOW, VINCE.

51:00.250 --> 51:03.417
DUDE, HER LEFT WRIST WAS
2 INCHES SHORTER THAN HER RIGHT.

51:03.417 --> 51:06.542
I MEAN, WHY CUT OFF MORE
ON THE LEFT SIDE THAN THE RIGHT?

51:06.542 --> 51:09.166
BECAUSE OUR GIRL...

51:09.166 --> 51:11.417
OUR GIRL WAS
A FUCKING AMPUTEE.

51:13.208 --> 51:15.750
I LOOKED UP
HER MEDICAL RECORDS.

51:15.750 --> 51:16.917
SHE HAD A FAKE LEFT HAND.

51:16.917 --> 51:18.667
THAT'S WHY
WE COULDN'T FIND IT.

51:18.667 --> 51:20.875
THE KILLER CUT OFF
THAT EXTRA PIECE OF WRIST

51:20.875 --> 51:22.500
SO THAT WE WOULDN'T SEE
THE STUMP.

51:22.500 --> 51:24.041
LET ME SEE THAT.

51:24.041 --> 51:25.917
THAT NIGHT
BATISTA WAS STABBED,

51:25.917 --> 51:28.333
HE WAS FOLLOWING UP
ON A LEAD HE GOT

51:28.333 --> 51:29.875
FROM A ONE-HANDED CALL GIRL.

51:29.875 --> 51:33.000
GUESS WHAT
THE LEAD WAS ABOUT.

51:33.000 --> 51:35.750
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

51:35.750 --> 51:37.208
BOOYAH.

51:41.917 --> 51:43.291
YOU SURE?

51:43.291 --> 51:45.750
POSITIVE. THE SAMPLES
YOU GAVE ME WERE A MATCH.

51:45.750 --> 51:48.208
THEY'RE FROM THE SAME PERSON.

51:50.375 --> 51:52.709
HEY, YOU ALL RIGHT?

52:00.083 --> 52:02.208
WHERE'S MY SISTER?

52:02.208 --> 52:05.083
TOOK HER CODE 12.
LEFT ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

52:05.083 --> 52:07.333
SHE WASN'T SUPPOSED
TO GO ANYWHERE.

52:07.333 --> 52:09.834
DISPATCH,
THIS IS DEXTER MORGAN.

52:09.834 --> 52:12.834
I NEED YOU TO RAISE OFFICER
DEBRA MORGAN ON HER RADIO.

52:17.417 --> 52:18.917
Man: SORRY, SIR.

52:18.917 --> 52:21.250
SHE'S BEEN OUT OF RANGE
FOR THE LAST HALF-HOUR.

52:23.667 --> 52:25.792
IT'S DEB. DO IT.

52:25.792 --> 52:27.291
WHERE THE FUCK ARE YOU?

52:27.291 --> 52:28.875
I'M HERE AT WORK,
AND YOU'RE NOT.

52:28.875 --> 52:30.083
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

52:30.083 --> 52:32.458
DO NOT SEE RUDY
UNTIL YOU FIND ME.

52:32.458 --> 52:34.583
CALL ME WHEN YOU GET THIS.

52:41.834 --> 52:43.750
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

52:52.375 --> 52:53.875
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

